### Fallback Strategies
```css
/* CSS Grid Fallback */
.services-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    display: grid; /* Override if supported */
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
}

/* Custom Properties Fallback */
.button {
    background: #a855f7; /* Fallback */
    background: var(--primary-purple, #a855f7);
}
```

